data.description: Huge reduction for quick sale, Come quick! PAID OFF SOLAR! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Lake Elsinore! This beautifully appointed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers an array of modern amenities, including a custom-built arcade-style game room and a paid-off solar panel system. Nestled in a prime location near parks, schools, and major freeways, this property promises both comfort and convenience. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow from the living area to the dining space, making it ideal for entertaining. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and an island with seating, making meal preparation a breeze. It's the perfect setting for culinary enthusiasts and family meals. The spacious master bedroom offers a serene retreat with an en-suite bathroom featuring dual sinks and a soaking tub. Outdoor built in patio is private sanctuary is a haven of relaxation after a long day. One of the standout features of this home is the custom-built arcade-style game room. Whether you're a gaming enthusiast or simply looking for a fun space to unwind, this room will surely delight you and your guests. Kids will automatically love it! Enjoy the benefits of a fully PAID OFF Solar Panel System, which not only reduces your energy bills but also minimizes your carbon footprint. It's also just down the street from the renowned Lake Elsinore Storm Stadium, perfect for sports enthusiasts. Refrigerator included with appliances! Don't miss the opportunity to make this Lake Elsinore gem your own. Whether you're looking for a place to call home or a fantastic investment property, this residence has it all. Schedule a viewing today to experience the magic of this exceptional listing firsthand.
